\v 1 Hawu maGalathiya ayizithutha, ngubani oliloyileyo\x + Seb. 16.6.\x* ukuze lingalaleli\x + 5.7.\x* iqiniso\x + 2.5,14. 4.16. Tit. 1.14.\x*\x + 5.7.\x*, lina abekwa obala phambi kwamehlo enu uJesu Kristu, ebethelwe phakathi kwenu\x + Nani 21.9.\x*?
\v 2 Yilokhu kuphela engithanda ukukufunda kini \add ukuthi\add*: Lemukela uMoya ngemisebenzi yomlayo yini\x + 3.14. Efe. 1.13. Seb. 2.38. 8.15. 10.44. 15.8. Heb. 6.4.\x*, loba ngokuzwa\x + Roma 10.17. Luka 7.1.\x* kokholo\x + 3.14. Efe. 1.13. Seb. 2.38. 8.15. 10.44. 15.8. Heb. 6.4.\x*?
\v 3 Kanti liyizithutha kangaka? Liqale ngoMoya\x + 4.9. Fil. 1.6.\x* selipheleliswa ngenyama yini?
\v 4 Lahlupheka izinto ezinengi\f + \fk ezinengi: \fl kumbe, \fq ezinkulu.\f* kangaka ngeze yini? Uba-ke ngitsho ngeze\x + 1 Kor. 15.2. Heb. 10.32,35,36. 2 Joha. 1.8.\x*.
\v 5 Ngakho yena olinika uMoya losebenza imisebenzi yamandla phakathi kwenu, \add kungaba\add* ngemisebenzi yomlayo yini, kumbe ngokuzwa kokholo\x + 2.8. 1 Kor. 12.10.\x*?
