\v 6 NjengoAbrahama wakholwa kuNkulunkulu, kwabalelwa-ke kuye ukuthi yikulunga\x + Gen. 15.6. Roma 4.3,9,21,22. Jak. 2.23. Roma 4.9,21,22.\x*.
\v 7 Ngakho liyazi ukuthi labo abangabokholo\x + 3.9,29. Roma 3.26.\x*, bona bangabantwana bakaAbrahama\x + Luka 19.9. Joha. 1.47.\x*.
\v 8 Lombhalo, ubona ngaphambili ukuthi uNkulunkulu\x + 3.22. 4.30. Roma 9.17. 10.11. Roma 1.2.\x* ulungisisa abezizwe ngokholo\x + Roma 3.30.\x*, watshumayela ivangeli ngaphambili kuAbrahama wathi: Izizwe zonke zizabusiswa kuwe\x + 3.16. Gen. 12.3.\x*.
\v 9 Ngakho abangabokholo babusiswa kanye loAbrahama okholwayo\x + 3.9,29. Roma 3.26.\x*.
