\v 10 Ngoba bonke abemisebenzi yomlayo bangaphansi kwesiqalekiso\x + 5.4. Roma 4.15. Mat. 5.19. Jak. 2.10.\x*; ngoba kulotshiwe \add ukuthi\add*: Uqalekisiwe wonke ongaqhubeki kukho konke okulotshiweyo encwadini yomlayo ukukwenza\x + Dute. 27.26. Jer. 11.3. Hez. 18.4.\x*.
\v 11 Kodwa kusobala ukuthi ngomlayo kakulamuntu olungisiswayo phambi kukaNkulunkulu\x + 3.24. 2.16.\x*; ngoba: Olungileyo uzaphila ngokholo\x + Hab. 2.4. Roma 1.17. Heb. 10.38.\x*;
\v 12 kodwa umlayo kawusiwo wokholo, kodwa \add kuthiwa\add*: Umuntu owenza lezizinto uzaphila kuzo\x + Levi 18.5. Roma 10.5.\x*.
\v 13 UKristu\x + 2 Kor. 5.21.\x* wasihlenga kusiqalekiso somlayo, esenziwe waba yisiqalekiso esikhundleni sethu\x + 4.5. 1 Kor. 6.20.\x*; ngoba kulotshiwe \add ukuthi\add*: Uqalekisiwe wonke\x + Dute. 21.23.\x* olenga esihlahleni\x + Seb. 5.30.\x*;
\v 14 ukuze kuthi isibusiso sikaAbrahama sifike kwabezizwe ngoKristu Jesu\x + Mat. 8.11.\x*, ukuze semukele\x + 3.2.\x* isithembiso sikaMoya ngokholo\x + Seb. 2.33. Isa. 44.3. Hez. 11.19. Jow. 2.28.\x*.
