\v 15 Bazalwane, ngikhuluma njengokomuntu\x + Roma 3.5.\x*; ngitsho isivumelwano somuntu\x + Roma 9.4.\x* esiqinisiweyo\x + 2 Kor. 2.8.\x*, kakho o\add si\add*chithayo loba o\add s\add*engezelelayo\x + 2.21. Mark. 7.9.\x*.
\v 16 Njalo izithembiso zakhulunywa\x + Seb. 13.32.\x* kuAbrahama lenzalweni yakhe\x + 3.8. Luka 1.55. Roma 4.16.\x*. Katsho \add ukuthi\add*: Lezinzalweni, njengokungathi zinengi, kodwa njengokungathi ngeyodwa \add ukuthi\x + Mat. 1.1.\x*\add*: Lenzalweni yakho, enguKristu\x + 3.19. Gen. 13.15. 17.8. 22.18.\x*.
\v 17 Lalokho ngiyakutsho: Umlayo oweza emva kweminyaka engamakhulu amane lamatshumi amathathu kawusesuli isivumelwano esaqiniswa nguNkulunkulu kuKristu ngaphambili\x + Gen. 12.1-3. 15.13. Eks. 12.40,41. Seb. 7.6.\x*, ukuze usenze isithembiso sibe yize\x + Mat. 15.6.\x*\x + Roma 4.14. Heb. 6.12.\x*\x + 5.4,11. 1 Kor. 13.8.\x*.
\v 18 Ngoba uba ilifa livela emlayweni, alisaveli esithembisweni; kodwa uNkulunkulu wa\add li\add*nika uAbrahama ngesithembiso\x + Roma 4.14. Heb. 6.12.\x*.
\s Umsebenzi womlayo
\p
\v 19 Pho, umlayo uyini? Wengezwa ngenxa yeziphambeko\x + Roma 4.15. 1 Tim. 1.9.\x*, kuze kufike inzalo eyanikwa isithembiso\x + 3.19. Gen. 13.15. 17.8. 22.18.\x*; wamiswa ngezingilosi\x + Seb. 7.53.\x* esandleni somlamuli\x + Eks. 20.19,21,22. Dute. 5.5,22,23,27,31. 33.2. Joha. 1.17.\x*.
\v 20 Kodwa umlamuli kayisuye woyedwa\x + 1 Tim. 2.5.\x*, kodwa uNkulunkulu munye\x + Roma 3.30.\x*.
\v 21 Pho umlayo uphambene lezithembiso zikaNkulunkulu yini? Phinde\x + 2.17.\x*! Ngoba uba wawunikiwe umlayo olamandla okuphilisa, isibili ukulunga ngabe kuvela ngomlayo\x + 2.21.\x*.
\v 22 Kodwa umbhalo\x + 3.8.\x* uvalele konke ngaphansi kwesono\x + 3.23. Roma 11.32. Roma 3.9.\x*, ukuze isithembiso\x + Roma 4.16. Seb. 10.43.\x* ngokholo lukaJesu Kristu siphiwe abakholwayo\x + Mark. 11.22.\x*.
