\v 23 Kodwa kungakafiki ukholo\x + 2 Kor. 3.13.\x*, sasilondolozwe ngaphansi komlayo\x + 2 Kor. 11.32.\x*, sivalelwe kuze kube sekholweni obeluzakwembulwa\x + 3.23. Roma 11.32. Roma 3.9.\x*.
\v 24 Ngakho umlayo\x + Mat. 5.17.\x* wawungumeluleki wethu kuKristu\x + 1 Kor. 4.15.\x*, ukuze silungisiswe ngokholo\x + 3.11. 2.16.\x*;
\v 25 kodwa selufikile ukholo\x + 2 Kor. 3.13.\x*, kasisekho ngaphansi kukameluleki\x + 1 Kor. 4.15.\x*.
\v 26 Ngoba lonke lingabantwana bakaNkulunkulu ngokholo kuKristu Jesu\x + 4.5. Joha. 1.12. Roma 8.15. 1 Joha. 3.1,2.\x*.
\v 27 Ngoba lonke elabhabhathizelwa kuKristu\x + Roma 6.3. Mat. 28.19.\x*, lembethe uKristu\x + Roma 13.14.\x*;
